<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Also, seeing as I have to spend 6 AA in the general skills anyway, I thought I would go this route.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
